    <values>
        <field>Description__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Event Monitoring is not capturing Login events. Failed login attempts, unusual login locations, and credential stuffing attacks are not being logged.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Impact__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Without login event monitoring, you cannot detect a breach in progress, investigate a compromised account, or reconstruct an incident timeline. Attackers can attempt unlimited logins without any audit trail.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Remediation__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Purchase Event Monitoring add-on if not already licensed and enable Login event type in Setup &gt; Event Manager. Configure Transaction Security policies to alert on suspicious login patterns.</value>
    </values>
